## Pros And Cons of Pulsedesk
A quick look at Pulsedesk's strengths and weaknesses to help you decide if it's the right fit
### Pros
* Unlimited automations & workflows
* Easy knowledge base creation
* Intuitive ticket management system
### Cons
* Fewer integrations compared to large competitors
* Limited scalability for large enterprises

## Frequently Asked Questions
Quick answers to common questions to help you better understand the product, features, and services.
* Does Pulsedesk offer an API? **Yes**, Pulsedesk provides an open API for integration.
* What language does Pulsedesk support? Pulsedesk is primarily available in **English** and **Portuguese**.
* What other apps does Pulsedesk integrate with? It integrates with **Jira Software**, **Zapier**, and **Active Directory**.
* Who are the typical users of Pulsedesk? Typical users include **e-commerce brands**, **SaaS teams**, **startups**, and **online retailers**.
* What level of support does Pulsedesk offer? It offers support via **email**, **call**, **live chat**, and a **knowledge base**.
* Does Pulsedesk have a mobile app? **Yes**, Pulsedesk offers a mobile application for **iOS** and **Android**.
* What types of pricing plans does Pulsedesk offer? The Pulsedesk price offers **3-month**, **6-month**, and **12-month** plans. Request a personalized Pulsedesk pricing quote for your business.

